description: Every time we shoot a model more than once, the level of intensity has to be taken up a notch. We can’t keep doing the same thing, at the same level, and expect the model to get better. They want to be pushed when they come here, and pushed is what they will be. The bondage is the toughest she has ever endured, and the torment takes her to her breaking point.
title: Day of Reckoning
